Article (3)

In carrying out its functions, the Authority shall pursue the following objectives:

-adopt an effective and competitive policy in the field of Health Insurance;

-protect the interests of all participants in the Health Insurance Scheme;

-ensure the optimal utilisation of Health Insurance Premiums for the level of services delivered under the Health Insurance Scheme;

-promote the safety of all participants in the Health Insurance Scheme; and

-issue periodicals explaining the Authority's policies, guidelines and procedures with respect to the implementation of the Health Insurance Scheme.

